# Suppress npm's audit summary at the end of `npm install`. The 6 remaining
# advisories are moderate-severity, accepted, and documented in SECURITY.md.
# Running `npm audit fix` against them silently downgrades next + drizzle-kit
# to ancient majors and introduces dozens of new vulnerabilities — see
# SECURITY.md for the incident details.
#
# Audit explicitly when you actually want to check:  npm audit
audit=false
